                            <comment id="456281" author="adilger" created="Fri, 16 May 2025 00:59:55 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;patch &lt;a href=&quot;http://review.whamcloud.com/14885&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;http://review.whamcloud.com/14885&lt;/a&gt; (&quot;&lt;tt&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-5092&quot; title=&quot;nodemap: transfer idmaps between MGS, MDT, OST&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;LU-5092&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;LU-5092&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; nodemap: convert member hash to a list&lt;/tt&gt;&quot;) removed the code in question.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="113450" author="green" created="Mon, 27 Apr 2015 03:11:46 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;and the same in lprocfs_add_nodemap_idmap_seq_write and lprocfs_del_nodemap_idmap_seq_write&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="113449" author="green" created="Mon, 27 Apr 2015 03:10:57 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Also in lprocfs_add_nodemap_range_seq_write:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div class=&quot;preformatted panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;preformattedContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre&gt;        rc = nodemap_add_range(name, nids);
        if (rc != 0)
                GOTO(out, rc = -EINVAL);

        if (rc == 0)
                rc = count;

out:
        return rc;
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Why do we need that last &quot;if&quot; again?&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
